2005-9-15  Alejandro Cornejo <acornejo1@users.sourceforge.net>
	* Merged bufWindow and glWindow into a single class
	* Added glX based window transparency

2005-5-28  Alejandro Cornejo <acornejo1@users.sourceforge.net>
	* Added Curve Routines (Hermite, Bezier, etc).
	* Added dimension independent Vector class.

2005-3-13  Alejandro Cornejo <acornejo1@users.sourceforge.net>
	* Separated image loading and saving routines into ImageLib to avoid
	  compilation delays and size bloat.
	* Added FixedPoint class to Math library.

2005-2-13  Alejandro Cornejo <acornejo1@users.sourceforge.net>
	* Added alarm function to Timer class to allow easier
	  event programming.
	* Added preliminar text support to Window class, currently
	  only fully implemented for glWindow.

2004-12-23 Alejandro Cornejo <acornejo1@users.sourceforge.net>
	* Splitted Socket, ServerSocket and InetAddress
	* Added Buffer class with MD5, SH1 and encryption
	  capabilities.
	* Added DatagramPacket class to encapsulate a Buffer and
	  a InetAddress object.
	* Added DatagramSocket for connectionless UDP
	  communications.

2004-12-05 Alejandro Cornejo <acornejo1@users.sourceforge.net>
	* Changed Image.convert method to allow image resizing
	  for up and down rescaling. Internally it uses glu
	  functions to performe rescale.

2004-09-24 Alejandro Cornejo <acornejo1@users.sourceforge.net>
	* Updated FreeImage to 3.4.0
	* Changed configuration script to better detect target host
	* Fixed gray scale image saving
	* Changed the error reporting in File.*

2003-06-08 Alejandro Cornejo <acornejo1@users.sourceforge.net>
	* Updated FreeImage to 3.3.0 and added script to
	  simplify Makefile.am creation for FreeImage
	* Added script to create binary distributions

2003-04-26 Alejandro Cornejo <acornejo1@users.sourceforge.net>
	* Added Directory to Util
	* Fixed error in File.seek
	* Added File loading to Image

2003-04-17 Alejandro Cornejo <acornejo1@users.sourceforge.net>
	* Finally removed LibMNG support (really unused and 
	  just bloated the library with 500K.
	* Changed FreeImage to use also autotools for a cleaner
	  distribution. This should simplify the porting procedure.

2003-04-10 Alejandro Cornejo <acornejo1@users.sourceforge.net>
	* Now Image, Util, Math and Window all lie in the
	  same namespace and the same shared library

2003-02-03 Alejandro Cornejo <acornejo1@users.sourceforge.net>
    * Changed all the library to make it more portable and
	easier to build with added modules.
	* Now uses autoconf, automake and pkg-config
